          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1695739974384-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1695739974384-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1695739974384-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>chives</strong> finely</p><p>Combine the <strong>chopped chives</strong> with your <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> and a generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong> in a small bowl</p><p>Add a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and stir it all together until all of the breadcrumbs are coated in the oil – this is your <strong>chive crumb</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1695739979197-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1695739979197-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
