        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the fish is cooking, combine a squeeze of<strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>lemon juice </strong>with your<strong> mayo</strong> in a small bowl</p><p>Season with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>lemony mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
