      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Top, tail, peel and chop your<strong> carrot[s]</strong> into batons</p><p>Add the <strong>carrot batons</strong> to a pot with a lid, with plenty of <strong>boiling water</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, cook for 3 min</p>",
